OL,5, A survey question asking schoolchildren
OL,6, to describe their body image has been  
OL,7, branded "crude and disrespectful".     
OL,9,FOptions include "much too fat", "much  
OL,10,Ftoo thin" or "about the right size".   
OL,12,FHolly Rhys-Ellis, 26, who developed an 
OL,13,Feating disorder when she was 11, said: 
OL,14,F"The way this has been done, I don't   
OL,15,Fthink it's very helpful."              
OL,17,FCardiff University, which was involved 
OL,18,Fin commissioning the survey,           
OL,19,Facknowledged "some parents and children
OL,20,Fwill have concerns".                   
